無衝突的兼職工作。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業住宅部行政總裁布少明回應查詢時證實，該行正進行Bottom榜放無薪假期機制，住宅部現時有約4,000名員工，早前已向業績最差的100名員工發出警告信，並落入Bottom榜，即現時有10名員工必須離職，55名員工須自行申請無薪假期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2195000/2196975/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2195000%2F2196975%2F1_1024.jpg&h=bf585513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2196975/%E3%80%90%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%EF%BC%9A55%25%E4%BD%8E%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD%E9%A1%8D%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E9%A0%88%E6%94%BE%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%913%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87?mtc=60011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2196975%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25AF%2592%25E5%2586%25AC%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25EF%25BC%259A55%2525%25E4%25BD%258E%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%25A1%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%25913%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%2581%2587%3Fmtc%3D60011&d=doj6XsUHDZa6Ii%2FNJf%2FJBaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=373f2ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2196975/%E3%80%90%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%EF%BC%9A55%25%E4%BD%8E%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD%E9%A1%8D%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E9%A0%88%E6%94%BE%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%913%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87?mtc=60011</a>"},{"pid":"aca3adb4347226dd3e238e255e0cd110f4d8bfbc","tid":800109,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"要跑數喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}